Time Train No. Print this Page Nanjing - Shanghai Train Schedule Departing toFrom The close location combining with the well-developed rail network connect Nanjing and Shanghai, the two major cities in East China tightly. The daily trains from Nanjing to Shanghai have strengthened the link between the two cities making passengers commute between Nanjing and Shanghai more easily. To plan a train trip to Shanghai from Nanjing, you can visit a Nanjing-Shanghai train schedule on China Highlights to find a suitable train from Nanjing to Shanghai. There are many daily trains going to Shanghai from Nanjing every day.
